      <li parentName="ul">{`Installing the PagerDuty app for Zendesk will add an incident command console to your Zendesk account. This console allows PagerDuty to create Zendesk tickets, sync priority, and update tickets in real-time.
`}{`[block:callout]`}{`
{
"type": "info",
"title": "Early Access",
